Name: Average duration of 'Completed + In Call' compared to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + In Call' activities in cases with 'Completed + Resolved' status
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Resolved occurs

Name: Average lead time before 'Completed + In Call' occurs after 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Median duration of 'Completed + In Call' across all cases
Longest duration of 'Completed + In Call' before transitioning to any other activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + In Call' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C2305210> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Completed + In Call' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Completed + In Call and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases ending with 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + In Call' in cases with 'Accepted + Wait - User' status before it
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Average duration between 'Completed + In Call' and 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Difference in average duration of 'Completed + In Call' between cases with 'High' impact and 'Low' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and the end of case grouped by the last value of impact filtered by the function ma == 'High' where ma is the last value of impact

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + In Call' during weekdays versus weekends
Variation in duration of 'Completed + In Call' over different years in the event log
